    "description": {
      "value": "<p>After laying this Trap it sits unmoving in a singular spot.</p><p>This trap triggers when a small, or larger creature moves onto the ground or the floor within 5 Feet. </p><p>When this trap is triggered, the triggering creature must succeed a Constitution Saving Throw, being Stunned until the end of their next turn on a failed save.</p><p>When this Trap is upgraded, all creatures in a 15-foot cube must make the saving throw.</p>",
